e=\"font-weight: 600;\">Tiredness and fatigue</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Vitamin B12 also contributes to normal energy release and the reduction of tiredness and fatigue.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">†For women of child bearing age the beneficial effect is obtained with a supplemental folic acid daily intake of 400µg for at least one month before and up to three months after conception.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><em>This information is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health professionals regarding any&nbsp;medical condition.</em></p></li></ul>', 20, '<br>', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2020-01-13 07:47:01', '2020-01-13 07:47:01', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0);
