(263, 'RSP4609DmT', 'normal', NULL, 0, 10, 29, NULL, NULL, 'London - Vitabiotics - Bổ sung vi chất cho thiếu niên Wellteen Him Plus', 'london-vitabiotics-bo-sung-vi-chat-cho-thieu-nien-wellteen-him-plus-rsp4609dmt', '1578884744twTbI0Hl.png', '15788847443YFVZ5Os.jpg', NULL, '56 Viên', '1', '0', NULL, 42, 42, '<p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">For studies, sports and busy social lives, Wellteen Him Plus is our maximum level of nutritional support for teenagers and young men in the Wellteen range.</p><ul class=\"expandable__content__productlist\" style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; position: relative; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><li style=\"padding-left: 24px; position: relative;\">Our trusted Wellteen Him formula plus daily Omega-3 capsules</li><li style=\"padding-left: 24px; position: relative;\">Includes DHA which helps maintain normal brain function and vision*</li><li style=\"padding-left: 24px; position: relative;\">Includes Panthothenic Acid which contributes to normal mental performance</li><li style=\"padding-left: 24px; position: relative;\">From the UK’s No.1 vitamin company</li><li style=\"padding-left: 24px; position: relative;\"><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Wellteen Him Plus</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Advanced nutritional support for teenagers and young men</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Today\'s young adults have more to live up to than ever before, with busy social lives, late nights and early mornings, studying and sports to juggle. Ensuring a healthy, balanced diet is essential but it\'s not always a priority in a hectic teenage lifestyle. Wellteen Him Plus has been developed especially for teenagers and young men aged 13-19 years, it provides a comprehensive range of vitamins, minerals, Co-Q10, botanical extract Lycopene, plus a high purity Omega-3 capsule. Omega 3 provides DHA which helps to maintain normal brain function and vision.&nbsp;A beneficial effect is obtained with a daily intake of 250mg of DHA.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Mental performance</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Wellteen Him Plus provides Omega-3 EPA/DHA capsules. High concentration Omega-3 fish oil provides DHA* (Docosahexaenoic acid) which contributes to the maintenance of normal brain function and vision. Produced to the highest standards of quality control, using advanced molecular distillation for added purity.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Wellteen Him Plus tablets include zinc, iron and iodine which contribute to normal cognitive function, whilst pantothenic acid contributes to normal mental performance to help support concentration levels when studying. Iron also contributes to normal formation of red blood cells &amp; haemoglobin and contributes to normal oxygen transport in the body to support cells and organs.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Teenagers and diet</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">An optimum nutritional intake during adolescence and young adulthood can help set the stage for lifelong health. Teenagers need to have sufficient vitamins and minerals to ensure healthy development during growth spurts, plus as they undergo significant physical and biochemical changes in their bodies, the necessity for nutrients greatly increases. The teenage years are perhaps the most significant in terms of hormonal change, and of course emotional stress.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Reduction of tiredness and fatigue</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Juggling studies, sports and a busy social life all takes its toll. Wellteen Him Plus includes vitamins B6, B12 and vitamin C which contribute to normal energy release and the reduction of tiredness and fatigue.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Immune support</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">A range of nutrients including zinc, selenium, iron, folic acid, vitamins B6 &amp; B12 and vitamin D contribute to the normal function of the immune system. Recent research has shown that optimum dietary levels of vitamin D may be higher than previously thought, Wellteen Him Plus provides an effective level of vitamin D with 800IU (20µg) of the preferred D3 form.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Bone health</span></p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Health research shows that even a short period of very strict \"dieting\" during early teens can lead to low bone density, which causes weak bones in later life. Between 12-17 years of age, up to 90 percent of adult bone mass is laid down, so this is not a time to limit the intake of calcium or vitamin D which help to maintain normal bone health.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">Wellteen Him Plus tablets include vitamin D and minerals such as magnesium and zinc which contribute to the maintenance of normal bone health. Vitamin D also helps the body with the absorption and utilisation of calcium from the diet.</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.647; text-align: justify; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Metropolis, Arial, sans-serif;\"><em>This information is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health professionals regarding any&nbsp;medical condition.</em></p></li></ul>', NULL, '<br>', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, '2020-01-13 10:05:44', '2020-01-17 17:33:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0),
